<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Security Alert: New Sign-In</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            background-color: #f8fafc;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
            padding: 40px 20px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #4b5563;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .alert-notice {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
        }
        
        .alert-notice h3 {
            color: #991b1b;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .alert-notice p {
            color: #7f1d1d;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        
        .login-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .login-details h3 {
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .detail-row {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: flex-start;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
            font-size: 16px;
        }
        
        .detail-row:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            width: 120px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #4b5563;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
            word-break: break-all;
        }
        
        .cta-section {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 40px 0;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            color: white;
            padding: 16px 32px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
            margin: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .cta-button.primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6 0%, #2563eb 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button.security {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ef4444 0%, #dc2626 100%);
        }
        
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        
        .security-tips {
            background-color: #eff6ff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin: 30px 0;
            border-left: 4px solid #3b82f6;
        }
        
        .security-tips h4 {
            color: #1e40af;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        
        .security-tips ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .security-tips li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #1e3a8a;
            padding-left: 25px;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .security-tips li:before {
            content: "üõ°Ô∏è";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-size: 14px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer a {
            color: #ef4444;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .content {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header {
                padding: 30px 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .greeting {
                font-size: 18px;
            }
            
            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
                gap: 5px;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                width: auto;
            }
            
            .detail-value {
                text-align: left;
            }
            
            .cta-button {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üîê Security Alert</h1>
            <p>New sign-in detected on your account</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello {{recipientName}},
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                We detected a new sign-in to your {{companyName}} account. If this was you, you can safely ignore this email. If you don't recognize this activity, please secure your account immediately by reviewing your security settings and changing your password.
            </div>
            
            <div class="alert-notice">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Account Access Alert</h3>
                <p>A new sign-in was detected on your account. Please verify that this activity was authorized by you. If you did not sign in, take immediate action to secure your account.</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="login-details">
                <h3>Sign-In Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Date & Time:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{loginDateTime}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">IP Address:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{ipAddress}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Location:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{location}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Device:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{deviceInfo}}</span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <span class="detail-label">Browser:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value">{{userAgent}}</span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="cta-section">
                <a href="{{dashboardUrl}}" class="cta-button primary">Go to Dashboard</a>
                <a href="{{securityUrl}}" class="cta-button security">Review Security Settings</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="security-tips">
                <h4>üõ°Ô∏è Security Best Practices</h4>
                <ul>
                    <li>Always log out from shared or public computers</li>
                    <li>Use strong, unique passwords for your account</li>
                    <li>Enable two-factor authentication if available</li>
                    <li>Regularly review your account activity and sessions</li>
                    <li>Never share your login credentials with anyone</li>
                    <li>Keep your browser and devices updated</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Didn't recognize this sign-in?</strong><br>
                If you did not authorize this sign-in, please secure your account immediately by changing your password and reviewing your security settings. Contact our support team if you need assistance or have concerns about unauthorized access.
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                <strong>Account Security:</strong> We take your security seriously and monitor all account activity. This notification is sent as a precaution to ensure your account remains protected. Thank you for helping us keep your account secure.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This sign-in notification was sent to {{recipientEmail}} for security purposes.</p>
            <p>If you have concerns about this activity, please contact our support team at <a href="mailto:{{supportEmail}}">{{supportEmail}}</a></p>
            <p>{{companyName}} Security Team</p>
            <p style="margin-top: 15px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This is an automated security notification. Please do not reply to this email.
            </p>
            {{#if unsubscribeUrl}}<p><a href="{{unsubscribeUrl}}">Unsubscribe from notifications</a></p>{{/if}}
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 